# rule.forbid.unbounded-recursive-globs

recursive globs (`**`) must exclude `node_modules`.

## .why

`**` with `cwd: process.cwd()` traverses node_modules (50k+ files) = OOM.

## .pattern

```ts
// bad
enumFilesFromGlob({ glob: '**/*.flag', cwd: process.cwd() });

// good
enumFilesFromGlob({ glob: '**/*.flag', cwd: process.cwd(), ignore: ['**/node_modules/**'] });
```

## .exception

scoped globs ok: `enumFilesFromGlob({ glob: '*.md', cwd: input.route })`

## .enforcement

unbounded `**` glob without ignore = **BLOCKER**
